/**
 * revert a document from server. The local document is replaced by server document
 *
 * @param {Object}
 *            config
 *            <ul>
 *            <li><b>domain : </b>{Fdl.OfflineDomain} the domain</li>
 *            <li><b>initid : </b>{Numeric} the document identificator</li>
